d narrowly here two back, before finishing third over 1400m in stronger company at Eagle Farm 17 days ago. That form reads well, and he looks to peak now, making him the one to beat. 1. WANTED HILLBILLY resumed at Ipswich over 1100m and was right there on the turn before peaking late to finish fifth. He has the pace to cross from the wide draw, and with a drop in grade, he will be fighting out the finish, especially with Ash Butler in the saddle. 2. MISTER MIGHTY caused an upset winning his maiden first-up here over this trip 4 weeks ago. He can secure the right run from the pole position, and he can take the next step immediately. 8. ELRONTE resumed with a solid effort for third at Ipswich before having no luck at Grafton from a wide gate. She gets a nice swing in her draw for her peak run, and if the track has some give in it, then she can bounce straight back into the money.\",\"runners\":[4,1,2,8],\"exclusive\":true}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Anthony Collins","tipRunnerNumbers":[3,1,4,2]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,8,1,3]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,8,10,4]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,8,2,6]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,2,4,8]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[8,3,4,2]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,8,1,2]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,8,3,2]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"TWB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"TWB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"TWB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"TWB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"TWB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venu